---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Marco Munich — Sviluppo siti e applicazioni web"
  description="Studio indipendente di Vicenza. Sviluppo siti e applicazioni web custom per chi vende se stesso. Niente template, niente abbonamenti mensili, codice pulito e file tutti tuoi alla consegna."
  currentPath="/"
>

<div class="ps4-page">
  <section class="ps4-hero">
    <div class="ps4-container">
      <div class="ps4-status-bar">
        <span class="ps4-pill"><span class="ps4-pulse"></span> ONLINE</span>
        <span class="ps4-pill">SYS · marco.dev</span>
        <span class="ps4-pill">v.2026.4</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="ps4-h1">
        <span class="ps4-h1__chrome">SITI.</span>
        <span class="ps4-h1__chrome ps4-h1__chrome--violet">APP.</span>
        <span class="ps4-h1__chrome ps4-h1__chrome--cyan">BRAND.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="ps4-hero__tag">
        Sviluppo siti e applicazioni per chi vende se stesso. Vengo da sette anni di personal branding olistico, oggi traduco quell'esperienza in codice. ✦
      </p>
      <div class="ps4-hero__ctas">
        <a href="/contatti/" class="ps4-btn ps4-btn--chrome">[ INIZIA UN PROGETTO ]</a>
        <a href="#cosa" class="ps4-btn ps4-btn--ghost">↓ Cosa costruisco</a>
      </div>
      <div class="ps4-window">
        <div class="ps4-window__bar">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
          <span class="ps4-window__title">marcomunich.com / index</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-window__body">
          <div class="ps4-cmd">$ cat hero.txt</div>
          <div class="ps4-output">Sviluppo siti veloci, sicuri, costruiti da zero.</div>
          <div class="ps4-cmd">$ ls projects/</div>
          <div class="ps4-output">yoga-studio  ristorante  ecommerce  booking  non-profit  ...</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ps4-section" id="cosa">
    <div class="ps4-container">
      <h2 class="ps4-section__title"><span class="ps4-arrow">▸</span> COSA COSTRUISCO</h2>
      <div class="ps4-services">
        <div class="ps4-card">
          <div class="ps4-card__head"><span class="ps4-card__num">[ 01 ]</span><span class="ps4-card__type">VETRINA</span></div>
          <h3 class="ps4-card__title">Siti vetrina.</h3>
          <p>Per professionisti, studi, attività locali. Costruiti sul tuo modo di lavorare e sul cliente che vuoi attirare.</p>
          <ul class="ps4-tags"><li>● Astro 5</li><li>● SEO ottimizzato</li><li>● Mobile-first</li><li>● Performance 100/100</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-card ps4-card--alt">
          <div class="ps4-card__head"><span class="ps4-card__num">[ 02 ]</span><span class="ps4-card__type">LANDING</span></div>
          <h3 class="ps4-card__title">Landing page.</h3>
          <p>Una pagina sola, costruita per convertire. Per lanci di prodotto, campagne pubblicitarie, raccolta contatti.</p>
          <ul class="ps4-tags"><li>● A/B test</li><li>● Analytics integrate</li><li>● Copywriting incluso</li><li>● Form custom</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-card ps4-card--alt">
          <div class="ps4-card__head"><span class="ps4-card__num">[ 03 ]</span><span class="ps4-card__type">SHOP</span></div>
          <h3 class="ps4-card__title">E-commerce.</h3>
          <p>Negozi online con pagamenti sicuri, gestione prodotti, integrazione Stripe o PayPal. Senza plugin che si rompono.</p>
          <ul class="ps4-tags"><li>● Stripe / PayPal</li><li>● Checkout custom</li><li>● Gestione ordini</li><li>● Email automatiche</li></ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-card">
          <div class="ps4-card__head"><span class="ps4-card__num">[ 04 ]</span><span class="ps4-card__type">APP</span></div>
          <h3 class="ps4-card__title">Web app custom.</h3>
          <p>Quando il sito normale non basta più. Dashboard, area riservata, automazioni, integrazione con API esterne.</p>
          <ul class="ps4-tags"><li>● FastAPI / Node</li><li>● Database SQL</li><li>● Auth & permissions</li><li>● Hosting incluso</li></ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ps4-section ps4-section--alt" id="lavori">
    <div class="ps4-container">
      <div class="ps4-section__head-row">
        <h2 class="ps4-section__title"><span class="ps4-arrow">▸</span> LAVORI · DEMO NAVIGABILI</h2>
        <a href="/portfolio/" class="ps4-link">// archivio completo</a>
      </div>
      <p class="ps4-section__lead">
        Una selezione di siti progettati come dimostrazioni del tipo di lavoro che faccio. Sono <span class="ps4-mark">demo</span>, non clienti reali. Ognuna è completamente navigabile.
      </p>
      <div class="ps4-projects">
        <a href="/portfolio/yoga-studio" class="ps4-pgrid"><span class="ps4-pgrid__year">[2026 · DEMO]</span><h3>yoga-studio</h3><p>Sito vetrina · prenotazioni · listino corsi</p><span class="ps4-pgrid__arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="/portfolio/ristorante" class="ps4-pgrid"><span class="ps4-pgrid__year">[2026 · DEMO]</span><h3>ristorante</h3><p>Vetrina · menu · storia · galleria foto</p><span class="ps4-pgrid__arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="/portfolio/ecommerce" class="ps4-pgrid"><span class="ps4-pgrid__year">[2026 · DEMO]</span><h3>ecommerce</h3><p>Catalogo · scheda prodotto · carrello · checkout</p><span class="ps4-pgrid__arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="/portfolio/booking" class="ps4-pgrid"><span class="ps4-pgrid__year">[2026 · DEMO]</span><h3>booking</h3><p>Studio professionale · area cliente · pagamenti</p><span class="ps4-pgrid__arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="/portfolio/non-profit" class="ps4-pgrid"><span class="ps4-pgrid__year">[2026 · DEMO]</span><h3>non-profit</h3><p>Storia · progetti · raccolta donazioni</p><span class="ps4-pgrid__arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="/portfolio/corso-online" class="ps4-pgrid"><span class="ps4-pgrid__year">[2026 · DEMO]</span><h3>corso-online</h3><p>Vendita corso · area studente · video lezioni</p><span class="ps4-pgrid__arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ps4-section" id="metodo">
    <div class="ps4-container">
      <h2 class="ps4-section__title"><span class="ps4-arrow">▸</span> METODO · COME LAVORO</h2>
      <div class="ps4-method">
        <div class="ps4-method__lead">
          <p>
            Non scrivo codice riga per riga. Guido <span class="ps4-mark">l'intelligenza artificiale</span> per costruire siti e applicazioni che funzionano. Risultato: stesso output di sviluppo tradizionale, più veloce e con meno errori.
          </p>
          <a href="/vibe-coding/" class="ps4-link">// come funziona, in pratica →</a>
        </div>
        <ol class="ps4-method__steps">
          <li><span class="ps4-step__id">[ 01 ]</span><h4>Capisco il progetto</h4><p>Una chiamata di 30 min per inquadrare cosa serve.</p></li>
          <li><span class="ps4-step__id">[ 02 ]</span><h4>Disegno la struttura</h4><p>Pagine, contenuti, logica. Tu approvi prima del codice.</p></li>
          <li><span class="ps4-step__id">[ 03 ]</span><h4>Costruisco</h4><p>Sviluppo iterativo con anteprime live. Niente sorprese.</p></li>
          <li><span class="ps4-step__id">[ 04 ]</span><h4>Consegno</h4><p>Codice nel tuo repository, file tutti tuoi, documentazione.</p></li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ps4-section ps4-section--alt" id="chi">
    <div class="ps4-container">
      <h2 class="ps4-section__title"><span class="ps4-arrow">▸</span> CHI SONO</h2>
      <div class="ps4-bio">
        <div class="ps4-bio__main">
          <p>
            Da sette anni lavoro su come ci si presenta online. Ho seguito coach, counselor, operatori olistici e professionisti di vario tipo nel costruire la loro presenza online.
          </p>
          <p>
            A un certo punto ho cominciato a costruire io stesso i siti, perché vedere coach con siti tutti uguali aveva stancato anche me. Oggi è quello che faccio principalmente: <span class="ps4-mark">siti e applicazioni costruiti su misura</span>, con uno sguardo che viene da anni di lavoro sul brand di chi li commissiona.
          </p>
          <a href="/servizi/posizionamento-online/" class="ps4-link">// vuoi solo la consulenza? →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-bio__sidecard">
          <div class="ps4-sidecard__row"><span class="ps4-sidecard__lbl">Studio</span><span class="ps4-sidecard__val">Marco Munich</span></div>
          <div class="ps4-sidecard__row"><span class="ps4-sidecard__lbl">Sede</span><span class="ps4-sidecard__val">Vicenza, IT</span></div>
          <div class="ps4-sidecard__row"><span class="ps4-sidecard__lbl">Esperienza</span><span class="ps4-sidecard__val">Dal 2019</span></div>
          <div class="ps4-sidecard__row"><span class="ps4-sidecard__lbl">Lingue</span><span class="ps4-sidecard__val">IT · EN</span></div>
          <div class="ps4-sidecard__row"><span class="ps4-sidecard__lbl">Stack</span><span class="ps4-sidecard__val"><a href="#stack" style="color:#00e5ff;text-decoration:none">// vedi sotto ↓</a></span></div>
          <div class="ps4-sidecard__row"><span class="ps4-sidecard__lbl">Disponibile</span><span class="ps4-sidecard__val ps4-avail">● Maggio 2026</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ps4-section" id="stack">
    <div class="ps4-container">
      <h2 class="ps4-section__title"><span class="ps4-arrow">▸</span> STACK · STRUMENTI</h2>
      <p class="ps4-section__lead">
        Il set di tecnologie con cui costruisco. Lo strumento giusto dipende dal progetto, ma queste sono le radici a cui torno.
      </p>
      <div class="ps4-stack">
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">Frontend</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">Astro · React · Tailwind CSS · TypeScript · Markdoc · Playwright</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">Backend</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">FastAPI · Uvicorn · Node.js · Python · PHP</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">Database & ORM</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">SQLite · SQLAlchemy 2 · MySQL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">CMS</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">Ghost CMS · Keystatic · WordPress (legacy)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">Pagamenti</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">Stripe · PayPal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">Email & Auth</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">Resend · JWT · itsdangerous (signed cookies)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">AI / LLM</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">Claude (Anthropic SDK) · Gemini · Imagen 4 · Veo 2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">Integrazioni API</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">Instagram (Graph API + instagrapi) · Telegram Bot · Open-Meteo · Spotify</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">Deploy & DevOps</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">Cloudflare Pages · Railway · GitHub Actions · PM2 · lftp</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ps4-stack__row">
          <span class="ps4-stack__lbl">Tooling</span>
          <span class="ps4-stack__val">Git · VS Code · Pillow · APScheduler · Jinja2</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ps4-section" id="contatti">
    <div class="ps4-container">
      <h2 class="ps4-section__title"><span class="ps4-arrow">▸</span> CONTATTAMI · PARLIAMONE</h2>
      <div class="ps4-contact">
        <div class="ps4-contact__intro">
          <p class="ps4-contact__lead">
            Una chiamata gratuita di trenta minuti. Capisco la tua situazione, ti dico se posso aiutarti davvero. Se non posso, te lo dico subito e ti indirizzo verso qualcun altro. ✦
          </p>
          <div class="ps4-contact__direct">
            <p class="ps4-contact__direct-lbl">// preferisci scrivere direttamente?</p>
            <a href="mailto:consulenza@marcomunich.com" class="ps4-contact__email">consulenza@marcomunich.com</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <form class="ps4-form" id="ps4-form" onsubmit="return ps4SubmitContact(event)">
          <div class="ps4-form__row">
            <label for="ps4-nome">// nome</label>
            <input type="text" id="ps4-nome" name="nome" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>
          <div class="ps4-form__row">
            <label for="ps4-email">// email</label>
            <input type="email" id="ps4-email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
          <div class="ps4-form__row">
            <label for="ps4-tipo">// tipo progetto</label>
            <select id="ps4-tipo" name="tipo" required>
              <option value="">— scegli —</option>
              <option>Sito vetrina</option>
              <option>Landing page</option>
              <option>E-commerce</option>
              <option>Web app custom</option>
              <option>Posizionamento online</option>
              <option>Altro / non sono sicuro</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="ps4-form__row">
            <label for="ps4-messaggio">// raccontami il progetto</label>
            <textarea id="ps4-messaggio" name="messaggio" rows="5" required placeholder="Cosa stai costruendo, a chi parla, cosa ti serve..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="ps4-btn ps4-btn--big">[ INVIA RICHIESTA → ]</button>
          <p class="ps4-form__note" id="ps4-form-note"></p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  function ps4SubmitContact(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    var nome = document.getElementById('ps4-nome').value;
    var email = document.getElementById('ps4-email').value;
    var tipo = document.getElementById('ps4-tipo').value;
    var msg = document.getElementById('ps4-messaggio').value;
    var subject = 'Nuovo contatto da ' + nome + ' — ' + tipo;
    var body = 'Da: ' + nome + ' (' + email + ')\nTipo progetto: ' + tipo + '\n\n' + msg;
    var mailto = 'mailto:consulenza@marcomunich.com?subject=' + encodeURIComponent(subject) + '&body=' + encodeURIComponent(body);
    window.location.href = mailto;
    document.getElementById('ps4-form-note').textContent = '// apertura del client email...';
    return false;
  }
</script>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Nascondi header, footer e padding-top del BaseLayout: la pagina ha nav e footer integrati */
  :global(.mm-header), :global(.mm-footer) { display: none !important; }
  :global(.pt-16) { padding-top: 0 !important; }
  :global(body) { padding-top: 0 !important; margin: 0 !important; }
  :global(main#main-content) { margin-top: 0 !important; padding-top: 0 !important; }

  .ps4-page { background: #0a0512; color: #f0e9ff; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; position: relative; min-height: 100vh; }
  .ps4-container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; width: 100%; position: relative; z-index: 2; }

  .ps4-bg { position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; overflow: hidden; z-index: 0; }
  .ps4-bg__blob { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(120px); opacity: 0.45; }
  .ps4-bg__blob--magenta { background: #ff2d92; width: 600px; height: 600px; top: 10%; left: -10%; animation: ps4float 18s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .ps4-bg__blob--cyan { background: #00e5ff; width: 500px; height: 500px; top: 50%; right: -8%; animation: ps4float 22s ease-in-out infinite reverse; }
  .ps4-bg__blob--violet { background: #8a3aff; width: 700px; height: 700px; bottom: -20%; left: 30%; animation: ps4float 25s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes ps4float { 0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0) scale(1); } 50% { transform: translate(40px,-60px) scale(1.1); } }

  .ps4-nav { background: rgba(10,5,18,0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(240,233,255,0.1); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50; }
  .ps4-nav__inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 1.1rem 0; }
  .ps4-logo { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; color: #f0e9ff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .ps4-logo__sym { color: #00e5ff; }
  .ps4-menu { display: flex; gap: 1.4rem; align-items: center; }
  .ps4-menu a { color: rgba(240,233,255,0.7); text-decoration: none; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: color 0.2s ease; }
  .ps4-menu a:hover { color: #00e5ff; }
  .ps4-menu__cta { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #b5b5b5 100%); color: #0a0512 !important; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 700 !important; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }

  .ps4-hero { padding: 5rem 0 6rem; }
  .ps4-status-bar { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .ps4-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; color: #00e5ff; background: rgba(0,229,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.4); padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 999px; }
  .ps4-pulse { width: 7px; height: 7px; background: #6ee870; border-radius: 50%; animation: ps4pulse 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes ps4pulse { 0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(110,232,112,0.5); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px transparent; } }
  .ps4-h1 { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(3rem, 11vw, 10rem); line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: -0.05em; margin: 0 0 2.5rem; }
  .ps4-h1__chrome { display: block; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #d8d8d8 25%, #909090 45%, #ffffff 55%, #f5f5f5 75%, #b5b5b5 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
  .ps4-h1__chrome--violet { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ff2d92 0%, #ffe2f0 30%, #8a3aff 70%, #4a0066 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; }
  .ps4-h1__chrome--cyan { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #00e5ff 0%, #b8faff 35%, #007a99 70%, #002a33 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; }
  .ps4-hero__tag { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.65; color: rgba(240,233,255,0.78); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 0 2.5rem; }
  .ps4-hero__ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 4rem; }

  .ps4-btn { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.05em; padding: 1rem 1.6rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; transition: all 0.2s ease; display: inline-block; }
  .ps4-btn--chrome { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #b5b5b5 100%); color: #0a0512; box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.4), inset 0 -3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid #fff; }
  .ps4-btn--chrome:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(255,255,255,0.7); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .ps4-btn--ghost { background: transparent; color: #f0e9ff; border: 1px solid rgba(240,233,255,0.4); }
  .ps4-btn--ghost:hover { border-color: #00e5ff; color: #00e5ff; }
  .ps4-btn--big { padding: 1.3rem 2.4rem; font-size: 1.05rem; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #cccccc 100%); color: #0a0512; box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,45,146,0.4); }
  .ps4-btn--big:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(255,45,146,0.7); }

  .ps4-window { background: rgba(10,5,18,0.6); border: 1px solid rgba(240,233,255,0.15); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; backdrop-filter: blur(20px); max-width: 600px; box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(138,58,255,0.25); }
  .ps4-window__bar { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 0.55rem 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(240,233,255,0.1); }
  .ps4-window__bar > span:nth-child(1), .ps4-window__bar > span:nth-child(2), .ps4-window__bar > span:nth-child(3) { width: 11px; height: 11px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .ps4-window__bar > span:nth-child(1) { background: #ff5f57; }
  .ps4-window__bar > span:nth-child(2) { background: #febc2e; }
  .ps4-window__bar > span:nth-child(3) { background: #28c840; }
  .ps4-window__title { margin-left: 1rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(240,233,255,0.55); }
  .ps4-window__body { padding: 1.5rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .ps4-cmd { color: #00e5ff; }
  .ps4-output { color: rgba(240,233,255,0.75); margin-left: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }

  .ps4-section { padding: 6rem 0; position: relative; }
  .ps4-section--alt { background: rgba(10,5,18,0.4); }
  .ps4-section__title { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: #ff2d92; margin: 0 0 3rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,45,146,0.3); }
  .ps4-arrow { color: #00e5ff; }
